FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778825170
OL,3,CZookeepers support injured monkeys in
OL,4,CKenya as part of conservation work
OL,6,FThe bridges are a vital intervention
OL,7,Fin the Diani Beach region, where
OL,8,Fmonkeys are frequently killed or
OL,9,Finjured by traffic and electrocution
OL,10,Ffrom power lines. Crossing the main
OL,11,Fcoastal road can be very dangerous,
OL,12,Fwith an average of 55 primates injured
OL,13,For killed by vehicles each year.
OL,15,FSam said: "The bridges are made from
OL,16,Fdurable chains and hosepipes and
OL,17,Fusually last around five years.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
