OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778825170
OL,3,CZookeepers support injured monkeys in
OL,4,CKenya as part of conservation work
OL,6,F"Their main purpose is to create safe
OL,7,Fcrossings over roads and power lines,
OL,8,Freducing the number of electrocutions
OL,9,Fand road accidents affecting local
OL,10,Fprimates. The team also work closely
OL,11,Fwith local power companies to insulate
OL,12,Felectrical cables too.
OL,14,FIn one week, the team responded to two
OL,15,Fseparate reports of monkeys
OL,16,Felectrocuted by power lines.
OL,18,FOne monkey's injuries were sadly too
OL,19,Fsevere, and the animal had to be
OL,20,Feuthanised.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778825170
OL,3,CZookeepers support injured monkeys in
OL,4,CKenya as part of conservation work
OL,6,FHowever, a female Angolan colobus
OL,7,Fmonkey was successfully monitored
OL,8,Fovernight before being returned to her
OL,9,Ftroop the following day, an experience
OL,10,FEmily described as one of the most
OL,11,Frewarding moments of the trip.
OL,13,FEmily said: "We watched her return to
OL,14,Fher troop and she was immediately
OL,15,Faccepted back again, which was
OL,16,Fincredible to see. That is not always
OL,17,Fguaranteed with primates, so to
OL,18,Fwitness a successful reunion like that
OL,19,Fwas really special.
OL,26,@uD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
