OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778825170
OL,3,CZookeepers support injured monkeys in
OL,4,CKenya as part of conservation work
OL,6,F"The team at Colobus Conservation
OL,7,Fgenuinely valued our input and
OL,8,Finvolved us in the decision-making
OL,9,Fprocess throughout rescues and
OL,10,Frehabilitation cases.
OL,12,F"Through our work at Drusillas, we
OL,13,Fhave a lot of experience in animal
OL,14,Fhusbandry and welfare, so we were able
OL,15,Fto share practical ideas that could
OL,16,Fhelp reduce stress and improve
OL,17,Frecovery for rescued animals."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@^O]
